msgstr "在重新開機前應該完成的工作"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/upgrading.dbk:1333
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "When <literal>aptitude dist-upgrade</literal> has finished, the "
